            <p>The problem was in the lazy $_browser and $_environment class members initialization based on the $_auto value. (see Zend_Locale::isLocale() method).</p>

<p>$_auto is actually initialized early (in the Zend_Locale constructor).</p>

<p>So $_browser and $_environment were never initialised.</p>

<p>I also found getDefault(), getEnvironment() and getBrowser() methods dont have to be static.</p>

<p>Thomas, please review this patch (CS-10029) and conform if it's OK</p>

